{"lemma":"جِزَّة","slug":"جِزَّة","root":"ج.ز.ز","root_slug":"ج-ز-ز","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ز-ز","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n5656","n5657"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%90%D8%B2%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5656","headword_ar":"جَزَّةٌ","root":"jz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single cutting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shearing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) See 1."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n5657","headword_ar":"جِزَّةٌ","root":"jz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of cutting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shearing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaz~ahu jz~apF HasanapF","text_ar":"جَزَّهُ جزَّةً حَسَنَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheared it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a good manner"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, TA.) [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajiz~apF","text_ar":"وَجِزَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"is omitted after"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajaz~apF","text_ar":"وَجَزَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"; so that the reading there is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaz~apF HasanapF","text_ar":"جَزَّةً حَسَنَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  Also, (S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jazazN","text_ar":"جَزَزٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juzaAzN","text_ar":"جُزَازٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juzaAzapN","text_ar":"جُزَازَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is cut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of dates: (K:) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fleece;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wool of a sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shorn"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in one year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) [and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hair of a goat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a camel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tim~apN","text_ar":"تِمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when shorn; a shorn crop of wool,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of goat's hair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of camel's hair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wool of a ewe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a ram,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when shorn, and not mixed with any other:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) so accord. to AHát: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wool not used after being shorn;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) in which last sense you say also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuwfN jazazN","text_ar":"صُوفٌ جَزَزٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jizazN","text_ar":"جِزَزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jazaAy^izu","text_ar":"جَزَايِزُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lh, K:) the latter like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraAy^iru","text_ar":"ضَرَايِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqoriDoniY jiz~apF","text_ar":"اَقْرِضْنِى جِزَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", without regard to the difference of the vowels [in the sing.]. (TA.) One says to another,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awo jiz~atayoni","text_ar":"اَوْ جِزَّتَيْنِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaA^an~ahu EaAD~N EalaY jiz~apK","text_ar":"كَاَنَّهُ عَاضٌّ عَلَى جِزَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lend thou me the wool of a sheep, or of two sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and the latter gives him the wool of a sheep, or of two sheep. (S.) And one says of a man with a large beard,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY jaz~apK","text_ar":"عَلَى جَزَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"As though he were biting"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the wool of a shorn sheep."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA: in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jazazN","text_ar":"جَزَزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","Lh"]}]}}